  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK495">
<l>neṭumpuṉaluḷ vellu mutalai yaṭumpuṉalu</l>
<l>ṇīṅki ṉataṉaip piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In deep water, a crocodile will conquer (all other animals); but if it leave the water, other animals will conquer it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
